{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Forgotten_Star",
  "title": "A Forgotten 'Star'",
  "summary": "A glittering reception fills the Main Mezzanine of the Black Krayt Swoop Arena on the eve of its first grand swoop race, drawing racers, executives, spies, and socialites into a crowded swirl of drinks and intrigue. The boastful racer Troy holds court with fellow pilots Selektah and Naldo, the shop-owner Benjawa, and his personal doctor Aerilaya, while StarShield CEO Rabid (Mr. Fox) quietly orders his marines into position and confronts the unwelcome senatorial aide Ozzle. At the center of the undercurrents is the enigmatic Venus -- once known as the Empress Juliet -- whose reunion with the Imperial Tsaran Joir, a man who spent days at her side, stirs forgotten emotion beneath his cold exterior. The shark-like Master Sergeant Webb stalks Joir through the crowd, finally confronting him directly, as Rabid presses Venus and Ozzle in a tense diplomatic standoff. Amid the comic mishaps of the Quarren Ressec, the clumsy Jager, and the bored marine Juan, the gathering teems with old loyalties, veiled threats, and racing bravado as Ment challenges Troy and calls out for anyone who wants to race but lacks a swoop.",
